{"tid":1363370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN：Liberate Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:49:44.000Z","uid":127479,"like":585,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"41d744e2fd3c058f6a3e41612c1c3c76560defc0","tid":1363370,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:05:08.000Z","msg":"繼鬼馬的美聯社後，輪到狡猾的CNN（今次不是fake news了）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>還記得我前日說《中英聯合聲明》失效後，會改為履行《南京條約》和《北京條約》嗎？CNN用地圖交代清楚，再配上一句：Liberate Hong Kong。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而所謂「回歸中國」，列出了兩個死穴：<br />\n<br />\n//No Hong Kong residents were party to the discussions, nor were they consulted about the final decision, which had a profound effect on their futures and freedoms.//<br />\n<br />\n然後，先講英治時代出世的人無路可逃，再將香港人分成00前出世和00後出世，說今日你如果18歲，到你46歲時，這個城市就會完全成為中國。<br />\n<br />\n接下來這樣說：<br />\n<br />\n//傳統上有兩種方法可以解決香港問題：通過立法機關或街頭抗議，但近年來這兩種方式都面臨越來越大的壓力，而且證明效果不佳。<br />\n<br />\n在中國推翻了英國殖民政府推出的最後一次民主改革方案之後，香港留下一個有缺陷的半民主制度，立法會50%是直選產生的，其餘由功能組別選出。企業集團往往強烈支持北京。這個城市的領導人不是由人民選舉產生，而是由北京主導的選舉委員會任命。//<br />\n<br />\n向外國讀者解釋為甚麼我們要爭取雙普選後，接下來這一段就講和平如何合理地轉化成激進暴力，老泛民怎樣被推倒：<br />\n<br />\n//Leung Yiu-chung, a 66-year-old pro-democracy lawmaker, was literally tackled out of the way as he attempted to prevent a makeshift battering ram being used to smash a door into the building.//<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">西環中聯辦，被稱為the Chinese government's headquarters in the city，而非Liaison Office。中央政府總部，中共政總，香港人要懂得這樣正名，否則，人們只會以為它只不過是一座中國大使館，忽略了它多年來怎樣干預和操控香港的高度自治。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n 最後一段，是記者對大家的鼓勵：<br />\n<br />\n//Whether Hong Kongers can achieve the democracy the city has spent decades fighting for is unclear, but for the young protesters taking to the streets, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>the window for doing so is shrinking, and the time to fight is now.//</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xr3sno4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxr3sno4.png&h=62b92f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition-m.cnn.com/2019/07/25/asia/hong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk/index.html?r=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition-m.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%3Fr%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=fe674431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition-m.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%3Fr%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F&h=905d471b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition-m.cnn.com/2019/07/25/asia/hong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk/index.html?r=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">左膠大報仲清醒過好多人<br />\n以後要將中聯辦正名做<strong>中共政總</strong><br />\n學劉細良話齋，香港政府一早已被架空，而家係<strong>中共政總</strong>治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"51e01aec3b651c644c0ea59b8cd9812cda42ee2f","tid":1363370,"uid":266036,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"中共政總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b7c778f2fd03456317254c6cd62c7a26f2f047","tid":1363370,"uid":261914,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"本全世界都已經覺得係中共策劃恐怖襲擊, 我哋唔好錯過依個機會<br />\n一定要加強依個信息比全世界知, 證實香港政府已經名存實亡！"},{"pid":"bab3adfab18872d4698043e26e860f2004bcd303","tid":1363370,"uid":133728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"大家幫手share出去啊<br />\n篇文好清楚咁道出咗主權移交談判香港人冇say 一國兩制 五十年不變失效 點解示威會由和平轉向勇武 同埋最新中共話有需要可以出解放軍<br />\n<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our times<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363088\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363088</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打打返中文分析比大家睇 呢篇文一定要share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabf2fc087f6c7da0abe881d23a2bd8adb8ee042","tid":1363370,"uid":66566,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our times</span>"},{"pid":"e170351693fa25791b661281aa14bcd0920742b3","tid":1363370,"uid":126731,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"the Chinese government's headquarters in the city<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5882e5f6b189c78a7559aee47bf3d2ff46e846","tid":1363370,"uid":81273,"like":9,"dislike":17,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"陳雲一早講緊liberate hong kong"},{"pid":"a1f45ab7aaeb2f3696ec3ea894edfc69137b43f2","tid":1363370,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fabf2fc087f6c7da0abe881d23a2bd8adb8ee042","tid":1363370,"uid":66566,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our times</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"era?"},{"pid":"2e3271119efec56c9ba518a3993aa8d1d4dd66ef","tid":1363370,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"好在住界限街以南。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e6dac2c491898523bb853f89f8924e9f555763","tid":1363370,"uid":266107,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"推到熱門<br />\n希望九龍 香港島畀人收返先"},{"pid":"41a13c63ddc89f8ddcdbbcd53698b217a56928ca","tid":1363370,"uid":75804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim